title: [Old Ta'Faendryl, West Woods]
description: Skirting the edge of a particularly dense tract of wood, the beaten footpath runs from the south to the northwest.  On each side of the path, gaps in the tree line reveal nothing but dark, murky shadows.

Skirting the edge of a particularly dense tract of wood, the beaten footpath runs from the south to the northwest.  On each side of the path, gaps in the tree line reveal little but brambles and the trunks of more trees.
